Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Md
Web Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Tactical Gloves Covert Black M
Web Item Description:
Precision feel and high dexterity are synonymous with 0.5mm palm protection. Our Specialty 0.5mm Covert shooting gloves are built to deliver natural feel and lightweight hand protection in an anatomical design. 0.5mm AX-Suede provides the perfect blend of tactile control and protection in the field or at the shooting range. Breathable TrekDry conforms to the back of your hands to reduce heat build-up and expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility for smooth manipulation.

Features:

  • Low-profile Thermoplastic Rubber (TPR) closure provides a secure fit to the wrist.
  • Lightweight TrekDry conforms to the back of the hand to reduce heat build-up and perspiration.
  • Anatomical stitch darts conform to the natural curvature of the hand to create a precision fit.
  • Expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility.
  • High-dexterity 0.5mm AX-Suede™ provides precision feel and high dexterity.
  • Nylon carrier loops.
  • Machine washable.

Item Name: Alps Grand Slam (Standard)

The ALPS Grand Slam Turkey Vest is the ultimate turkey hunting vest on the market today.   • Five shell loops
  • Hydration compatible
  • Large game bag
  • Two side/water bottle pockets
  • Two mesh zippered pockets inside of vest
  • Side compression straps adjust to different body types

Item Name: Alps Impact Pro Vest
Web Item Name: Alps Outdoorz Impact Pro Turkey Hunting Vest Mossy Oak Original Bottomland
Web Item Description:
The Impact Pro has all the innovative features and essential conveniences of the original Impact with a series of bolstering upgrades that the serious turkey hunter will appreciate. The sit-anywhere design of the flip down seat now features a 1" molded and ergonomic foam design with dual-aluminum stays that is ideal for long sits. Both front panels feature molded pockets for added protection for your calls and gear. Each panel also includes a series of MOLLE webbing to allow you to customize your loadout with a number of different ALPS accessories. Speaking of accessories included with the Impact Pro is a redesigned box call pocket and an accessory ThermaCELL pocket both removable and both able to be mounted to either of the front panels.

Reinforced double and triple stitching ensures both comfort and durability when you need it most. Enjoy your hunt with this premium turkey vest and its XL game bag decoy stake pocket 8 gear pockets including one oversized rear storage pocket contoured shoulder strap design and many more features aimed to please the hardcore turkey enthusiast.

  • Smooth durable reverse-coil YKK zippers throughout
  • Suggested temperature range: 35°F to 60°F with layering as needed

Muddy’s all-new Timber Recon Extreme (TRX) series hunting apparel will ensure you stay as dry warm and protected as you would be at home on the couch even when you couldn’t be farther from it. Boasting a 10k/10k waterproof and breathability rating our TRX Lightweight Rain Pants deliver a soft silent brushed tricot outer shell construction with breathable mesh lining that helps you stay comfortably cool and dry. Articulated knees help promote full freedom of movement. Thanks to two hand pockets large cargo pockets and back pockets you’ll have ample storage space for carrying every piece of essential gear necessary. And when the sky really opens up adjustable half-zip leg openings accommodate sliding this protective rain layer over top of your favorite hunting pants without ever removing your boots.

Item Name: Higdon Versa Vest (MO Original Shadowgrass)
Web Item Name: Momarsh Versavest Dog Vest Mossy Oak Original Shadowgrass
Web Item Description:
One Vest that REALLY fits every gun dog - for LIFE! Say goodbye to dangerous ill-fitting dog vests forever. MOMARSH's team of professional designers vets and sporting dog professionals have spent years engineering the world's best dog vest with the mission to do just one simple thing... FIT YOUR DOG.  With its Ultra-strong premium hook and loop adjustments The MOmarsh Versa-Vest properly fits your dog and changes with its shape and size over its lifespan. Six points of multi-directional adjustability ensure proper fit and sizing. Tough rubberized chest panel for ultimate protection. Stow-away handle and leash anchor. The MOmarsh Versa-Vest can be adjusted to be smaller or larger than any waterfowl dog vest on the market. Fits any dog from 35 to 100+ LBS. No Measuring No Cutting No Guessing.  Once the vest is initially adjusted to fit your dog properly simply use the over-sized zipper to take it on and off. No additional adjustments should need to be made until your dog changes shape or size.  Interchangeable cover panels available in other colors (sold separately) are removable replaceable and machine washable. Gore Optifade Waterfowl Marsh cover panels included. The Innovative Versatile Extraordinary Momarsh Versa-Vest. Engineered by Veterinarians Hunters and Sport-Dog professionals to FIT EVERY DOG... FOR LIFE.  

VERSATILE. ONE VEST THAT FITS EVERY SPORTING DOG.

Features:

  • VERSA-VEST can be adjusted to be smaller or larger than any existing sporting dog vest on the market. Fits any dog from 35 to 100+ LBS.
  • BUILT TO REALLY FIT YOUR DOG. 6 points of multi-directional adjustability to ensure proper fit and sizing. Ultra-strong premium hook and loop adjustments. Changes with the shape and size of your dog over its lifespan.
  • SAFE. Helps dog retain body heat in cold or wet conditions. Tough rubberized chest panel for ultimate protection where your dog needs it most. The Built in premium paracord handle and metal leash loop can stow away when not needed.
  • RUGGED. Built tough with high-quality 5mm rubberized Neoprene and water-repellent coated 600D poly fabric.
  • CUSTOMIZABLE. Interchangeable VERSA-VEST PANELS are available in a variety of colors. Panels are removable replaceable and machine washable (sold separately). 

Specifications:

  • One Vest that REALLY fits every gun dog
  • Engineered by Veterinarians
  • Helps dog retain body heat in cold or wet conditions.
  • Six points of multi-directional adjustability
  • Tough rubberized chest panel
  • No Measuring No Cutting No Guessing
  • Fits most dogs from 35 to 100+ lbs
  • Gore Optifade Waterfowl Marsh camo

Item Name: Arcus Insulated Vest Charcoal M
Web Item Name: Leupold Arcus Insulated Vest Charcoal M
Web Item Description:
Built for cold-weather hunts the Arcus Insulated Vest delivers warmth without the weight. It packs 120 grams of recycled synthetic insulation into a quiet low-bulk design with stitchless quilting that seals in heat and cuts the wind. Wear it under a shell or on its own—this vest is built to perform when temperatures drop.

Designed for versatility the Arcus features a durable 4-way stretch fabric with a PFAS-free DWR finish that sheds light rain and snow. Its 91/9 polyester-spandex blend enables full range of motion while an adjustable hem seals in warmth on demand. High-set zippered hand pockets remain accessible under a pack belt and fitted cuffs keep things streamlined. Finished with durable silicone logos and clean lines this piece delivers advanced performance without the weight or the waste.

Item Name: NOMAD AMBUSH CAMO LS MO BOTTOMLAND L
Web Item Name: Nomad Ambush Camo Long Sleeve Shirt Mossy Oak Bottomland L
Web Item Description: New school tech with old school looks the Ambush shirt sets itself apart by delivering incredible performance while still looking sharp. Honed over years of hunting in the South our Ambush shirt is purpose built for guys that get after it. The lightweight UPF 30+ synthetic fabric is built with inherent stretch that allows full range of motion with shouldering a shotgun or drawing a bow. Laser perforation venting throughout the back and total wicking performance will keep you cool and comfortable when you get that response to your call and the fever starts to kick in. The integrated eyewear wipe has incredible utility when you need to clean lenses whether its binos rangefinders or scopes in the field to your sunglasses for the drive home. The Ambush shirt is a woods hunter classic made better.

Item Name: Browning SHT MONROE 1/4 ZIP OVIX M
Web Item Name: Browning Monroe 1/4 Zip Long Sleeve Shirt Ovix Camo M
Web Item Description:
Climate conditions are one of the biggest hurdles to overcome as a hunter. Whether it's the high country or hardwoods mornings can be cold and afternoons searing hot and humid. And variables like a breeze from the north or a blanket of clouds can keep the weather unpredictable all day long. Of course this just underscores the importance of proper layering and the need of the Monroe 1/4 Zip Shirt.

This 2 layer piece is constructed with a tough dura knit fleece outer and a warm fleece inner surface for the perfect combination of durability warmth and stretch-enhanced comfort. The addition of a DWR coating offers water resistance making the Monroe extra versatile as both an outer piece in warmer conditions and an ideal insulation layer under a parka.  

Features:

  • 2L dura knit fleece
  • Water-resistant DWR coating
  • SILVADUR technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • Front 1/4 zipper
  • Left chest zippered accessory pocket
  • Elastic bound cuffs with thumb loops
  • Ovix Camouflage

Item Name: PNT WW FIELD PRO MOBL 36
Web Item Name:
Browning Field Pro Pant Mossy Oak Bottomland 36",

The Field Pro pant is versatile and comfortable making it a great addition to your hunting gear selection. Engineered with a 2L soft shell stretch fabric this pant is built for warmer weather waterfowl hunting with the right combination of durability wind and water resistance and just the right amount of stretch to optimize comfort. A DWR coating adds a level of water resistance. The soft inner lining adds comfort and warmth.

The Field Pro pant includes front and rear pockets plus a pair of cargo pockets on the thighs to keep your gear within easy reach. 13" long leg vents with zippered closures help keep you cool when the weather warms up or your activity level rises. Four-point knee articulation maximizes comfort and freedom of motion when getting into or out of your layout blind or walking along river banks. The comfortable cut allows for a base layer to be comfortably worn making the Field Pro pant an excellent outer layering piece for cooler drier weather.

Features:

  • Polyester stretch twill fabric with a soft backing
  • Highly wind resistant
  • Water-resistant DWR coating
  • SILVADUR technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • Deep zippered cargo pockets
  • Hand and rear pockets
  • 5 large belt loops
  • Side leg venting with 13" zippers
  • 4-point knee articulation for ease of movement
  • Size 32-40 with 32" inseam
  • Size 34-38 with 34" inseam

Item Name: Rugged Rare Elegant & Armed Concealed Carry Camisole (S)
Web Item Name: Cameleon Elegant & Armed Concealed Carry Camisole Black S
Web Item Description:
The Concealment Camisole was designed to be graceful and flowy yet structured enough to decrease “printing” or showing an outline of the gun through your clothes. Make it your own by dressing it up or down and pairing it with your favorite holster.

How to use:

Simply wear it overtop of your preferred holster and firearm for optimal concealment.

How it works:

Our patent-pending multi-layer design ensures the best possible concealment. The substantial underlayer is reinforced by eight panels – often called our 360-degree printing shields- that work to prevent an outline of the gun from showing through clothing.  The material on top creates dimension and movement further softening the appearance of any sharp edges. This innovative design creates a sleek look while providing you with the protection you need.

What holsters are compatible with the camisole?

Bellybands Kydex holsters the Enigma holster and even bra holsters.

Care Instructions:

Material- 100% Polyester
Lace- 90% Nylon 10% Spandex
Gentle cycle cold water air dry or tumble dry (low heat) steam or iron

Web Item Description:
The LimbSaver Shooting Vest is the ultimate solution for shooters who are looking for a way to reduce the intense kickback from their firearm. Whether you're an experienced shooter or just starting out this vest is designed to provide maximum comfort and protection.

With its protective shoulder pad made from LimbSaver's cutting-edge NAVCOM technology this shooting vest effectively reduces felt recoil making it ideal for extended shooting sessions or when using firearms without recoil pads. The NAVCOM material works by dissolving energy and vibration ensuring that your shoulder is protected from the toughest recoil.

Wearing the LimbSaver Shooting Vest is effortless simply slip it over your shoulder and clip it on. The vest is also compatible with LimbSaver recoil pads so you can experience the ultimate in recoil reduction.

So if you're looking for a way to reduce felt recoil and improve your shooting experience look no further than the LimbSaver Shooting Vest. Get yours today and start shooting with confidence!
